description.value: This value set represents conditions and diagnoses that identify non live births or deliveries such as fetal death, abortions or miscarriages. Please see VSAC (https://vsac.nlm.nih.gov/) for the latest expansion of the value set Non Live Birth Diagnosis 2.16.840.1.113762.1.4.1166.137 which contains ICD-10 and SNOMED CT values referenced in this grouping.

purpose.value: This purpose of this value set is to provide a list of terms that represent conditions and diagnoses that identify non live births or deliveries such as fetal death, abortions or miscarriages
